                     <summary>S face,relief. Landscape as background. On the left side is a cross, in front of which stands an elderly woman, who is handing something to a little girl standing in front of her. The little girl stretches out her hand to receive the something. The elderly woman is carrying a handbag in her right hand. Behind ( on the right side of) the little girl stand two adult persons: a woman and an old, bent man leaning on his stick, a bundle on his back. The little girl and the two women wear long dresses of a thick, heavy material ---and shawls. Poor people.</summary>
