   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="inscription" xml:lang="en" decls="#f_S #c_3 #m_I #t_P">
            <ab>IN LOVING MEMORY OF</ab>
            <ab>GEORGINA HARRIETTE</ab>
            <ab>WIFE OF F.A. SEARLE OF S. ANTONIO. TIVOLI.</ab>
            <ab>WHO WENT HOME 26 MARCH 1902. AGED 73 YEARS.</ab>
            <ab/>
            <ab>THE KINGDOM OF HEAVEN IS AT HAND</ab>
         </div>
         <div type="inscription" xml:lang="en" decls="#f_S #c_3 #m_I #t_S">
            <ab>ALSO</ab>
            <ab>OF FREDERICK AUGUSTUS SEARLE HER HUSBAND</ab>
            <ab>BORN AT SAFFRON WALDEN DEC.5.1824</ab>
            <ab>HE LIVED OVER 30 YEARS IN THE W. INDIES</ab>
            <ab>25 YEARS AT S.ANTONIO.TIVOLI.</ab>
            <ab>DIED AT RUSHMERE SUFFOLK SEP 10.1903.</ab>
            <ab>BLESSED IS THE MAN WHOSE STRENGTH IS IN THEE</ab>
            <ab>THY COMMANDMENT IS EXCEEDING BROAD</ab>
         </div>
         <div type="inscription" xml:lang="en" decls="#f_S #c_3 #m_I #t_S">
            <ab>ALSO</ab>
            <ab>OF THE REV. FREDERICK CHARLES SEARLE M.A. THEIR SON</ab>
            <ab>BORN MAY 5. 1859. HE DIED AT TIVOLI JULY 23. 1904</ab>
            <ab>MUCH LOVING MUCH LOVED</ab>
            <ab>HE WAS FOR OVER 17 YEARS</ab>
            <ab>AS ASSISTANT MASTER AT HARROW</ab>
            <ab>THE DEVOTED SERVANT AND FRIEND OF THE SCHOOL.</ab>
            <ab/>
            <ab>"THE GOOD SHEPHARD GIVETH HIS LIFE FOR THE SHEEP" S. JOHN X,II</ab>
         </div>
         <div type="inscription" xml:lang="en" decls="#f_T #c_3 #m_I #t_S">
            <ab>IN MEMORY OF GEORGE HANLEY HALLAM SON OF CHARLES AND MARTHA HALLAM</ab>
            <ab>BORN AT SHREWSBURY AUGUST 5TH 1846</ab>
            <ab>EDUCATED AT SHREWSBURY SCHOOL SCHOLAR OF ST. JOHN'S COLLEGE CAMBRIDGE</ab>
            <ab>FOR 37 YEARS CLASSICAL AND SOMETIME SENIOR MASTER AT HARROW SCHOOL</ab>
            <ab>HE MARRIED GEORGINA LOUISA SEARLE AND MADE S. ANTONIO TIVOLI HIS HOME WHERE HE DIED</ab>
            <ab>JULY 12TH 1932</ab>
         </div>
         <div type="inscription" xml:lang="en" decls="#f_T #c_3 #m_I #t_S">
            <ab>IN LOVING MEMORY OF GIORGINA DAUGHTER OF FREDERICK AND GEORGINA SEARLE</ab>
            <ab>WIFE OF GEORGE HALLAN</ab>
            <ab>BORN AT NICKERIE, GUINEA 24TH JULY 1863</ab>
            <ab>DIED AT SANT'ANTONIO, TIVOLI 11TH JUNE 1944</ab>
         </div>
